Title: Commending Ava Horton, Meka Bonsie-Machin and Emily St. John upon the occasion of their designation as recipients of a Liberty Medal
ActClause: LEGISLATIVE RESOLUTION commending Ava Horton, Meka Boncie-Machin and Emily St. John upon the occasion of their designation as recipients of a Liberty Medal, the highest honor bestowed upon an individual by the New York State Senate
